data.text:
CB Skin Secrets is located in Suite 500 of the Harvester Artspace Lofts 1 story commercial building on the east side at 1010 S Main Street in Council Bluffs.

To completely avoid the potential for train track delays, coming from Kanesville or Broadway in Council Bluffs, turn South on Pearl (which becomes S. Main Street). Or if you are coming from I-80 or I-29, take the Manawa exit aka South Expressway through Council Bluffs, go over the viaduct, turn East (right) on 5th Ave then South (right) on S. Main Street.

The 2hr parking is free on S. Main Street between 10th and 11th Ave. Enter the 1 story commercial building of the Harvester Artspace through door 2 (2 is painted on the building) by my light blue metal sign and the Any Age Guitar sign (the signs may not shown on Google Maps street view but it is the door behind the streetlight).

Loess Hills Floral suites 600-800 are further North in the same building but do NOT connect to my area interiorly so please do NOT use door 1. (Please note that despite corrections attempted, some old map links/apps may erroneously direct you to Jennie Edmundson Hospital instead of the newer clinic site which is NOT part of the hospital campus).

Thanks! If you have trouble with directions, you are welcome to try texting or calling me at 402-915-2756 for assistance. Please understand that I may be unable to answer immediately if I am with another patient.

CB Skin Secrets

1010 S Main St., Suite 500

Council Bluffs, IA 51503

402-915-2756
